  "description": "Configure farmland trample height ( gamerule )",
  "body": "<p><del></del>A simple fabric mod that adds gamerules to change farmland trample height.<br /><br /></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Gamerules : </span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><em><strong><span style=\"font-family: georgia, palatino, serif;\">trampleFallHeight</span>&nbsp;</strong></em><span style=\"font-size: 10px;\">( Default: 2<span style=\"font-size: 8px;\">( blocks )</span>&nbsp;)<span style=\"font-family: 'comic sans ms', sans-serif;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: 12px;\">: Trample fall height</span></span></span></span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><em><strong><span style=\"font-family: georgia, palatino, serif;\">doFarmlandTrample</span>&nbsp;</strong></em><span style=\"font-size: 10px;\">( Default: true )<span style=\"font-family: 'comic sans ms', sans-serif;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: 12px;\">: Enable/Disable farmland trampling</span></span></span></span></li>\n</ul>\n</blockquote>\n<br />Any issues? Comment down below or create an issue on github!<br /></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10px;\">This mod is a server-sided mod. It works both on server and client.</span><br /></strong></em></h5>",
